ions with moderate conditions (including magnetic field)\nwhere the typical values of several important parameters are consistent with\nobservations. We discuss the challenges of developing numerical extrapolation\nMHD codes in view of nonlinear degeneracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jan 2014 20:54:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-05"}
